   527в†’## API Design Standards
   528в†’
   529в†’### RESTful Conventions
   530в†’
   531в†’```typescript
   532в†’GET    /api/v1/users           # List users
   533в†’GET    /api/v1/users/:id       # Get user by ID
   534в†’POST   /api/v1/users           # Create user
   535в†’PUT    /api/v1/users/:id       # Update user (full)
   536в†’PATCH  /api/v1/users/:id       # Update user (partial)
   537в†’DELETE /api/v1/users/:id       # Delete user
   538в†’```
   539в†’
   540в†’### Response Format (Standard)
   541в†’
   542в†’```typescript
   543в†’// Success response
   544в†’{
   545в†’  "success": true,
   546в†’  "data": { /* payload */ },
   547в†’  "meta": {  // Optional
   548в†’    "page": 1,
   549в†’    "limit": 20,
   550в†’    "total": 100
   551в†’  }
   552в†’}
   553в†’
   554в†’// Error response
   555в†’{
